### Register a new user
POST http://localhost:4000/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "John Doe",
  "email": "john@example4.com",
  "password": "strongPassword123"
}

###

### Login
POST http://localhost:4000/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "john@example4.com",
  "password": "strongPassword123"
}

###

### Refresh access token
POST http://localhost:4000/auth/refresh
Cookie: refreshToken=eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJpZCI6IjZ2Xy1fQThqYnhpZXJIcWE2RlNIRiIsImlhdCI6MTc3ODA3NDQ3MSwiZXhwIjoxNzc4Njc5MjcxfQ.aUvMz89Db5qxpUBlyq4k5IgM5EjFogx5A1Cb7SZ3IYQ

###

